column5: and only AK has HUGE fish.... HAHAHAHA.... nice report brother.. I look forward to the pics!  Gerritt.
That sounds extreme in every way!  Get those pictures up soon. Thanks for the report.
Man, that's some report! Glad you did well in spite of the less than favourable weather. Looking forward to the pics. Thanks for the report.
I'll put up with snow for a 46" pike and 1499 other fish.  Sounds like a great time, cant wait for the pics.
